{
  "texts": [
    "Most of the reviewed surveys have considered studies that apply ML techniques, and a few of them have considered studies that used DL techniques to predict student's academic performance.",
    "Previous reviews generally covered the use of DL techniques and did not emphasize the contribution of hybrid techniques in improving the prediction's accuracy.",
    "Moreover, most articles in this area do not emphasize the necessity of integrating various feature categories.",
    "This review focuses on the most recently published articles that have applied either one or more DL techniques, or combined DL with ML techniques to predict student's academic performance.",
    "Additionally, it describes the datasets used and then discusses the importance of integrating various feature categories to identify the best qualities suitable for algorithm adaptation and to increase its accuracy."
  ]
}